output_sparql:
prefix bif: <http://www.openlinksw.com/schemas/bif#>
prefix brt: <https://brt.basisregistraties.overheid.nl/top10nl2/def/>
prefix geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
select ?place ?wgs {
  bind(?point as ?point0)
  ?place a brt:PlaatsRegistratie;
    brt:geometrieVlak ?rd.
  bind(bif:ST_Transform(?rd, 4326) as ?wgs)
  filter(bif:st_within(?point0, ?shape))
}
limit 1
